Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.32,0:22:29.12,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢動いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.35,0:22:34.54,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人の鼓動触れた時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.76,0:22:41.41,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねぇ　今誰を思っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.76,0:22:49.15,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硝子星に眺めた切ないその横顔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.41,0:22:55.39,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微かな距離でも届かなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.63,0:22:59.99,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言い訳ばっかりを束ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.25,0:23:02.95,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今を逃げてた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.13,0:23:06.34,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱虫だったあの頃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.59,0:23:14.34,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩れそうな弱さと向き合える気がしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.53,0:23:18.07,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出すよ 明日の扉開けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.32,0:23:21.74,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君が居る場所まで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.98,0:23:28.92,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃し続けてきた思い伝えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.12,0:23:36.21,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,here in my house君が笑う 何気ない世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.47,0:23:45.39,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞こえるその声が 私の涙強くする
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:49.14,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you are my only shooting star
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.32,0:22:29.12,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想開始悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.35,0:22:34.54,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我們觸碰到彼此的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.76,0:22:41.41,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你正在想念誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.76,0:22:49.15,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透過玻璃星星看到你的側臉 讓人如此無法割捨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.41,0:22:55.39,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使近在咫尺 卻也無法向你傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.63,0:22:59.99,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出種種借口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.25,0:23:02.95,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避著現實
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.13,0:23:06.34,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時的我如此膽小
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.59,0:23:14.34,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在終於鼓起勇氣直面那潰不成軍的軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.53,0:23:18.07,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發吧 打開通向明天的門扉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.32,0:23:21.74,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往你所在的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.98,0:23:28.92,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想向你傾訴那份一直未說出口的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.12,0:23:36.21,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這坦誠相對的世界裡 向我微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.47,0:23:45.39,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你的聲音 讓我的眼淚也變得堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:49.14,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是劃過我生命唯一的流星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.89,0:00:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼看待一個身為人妻的學生？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得行得通
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.22,0:00:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行得通？怎樣行得通？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥叫「怎樣行得通」啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.85,0:00:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道渡邊雷昂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.86,0:00:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個格蘭托奈爾財團的總帥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.95,0:00:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年已經65歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.48,0:00:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人不怎麼離開巴黎生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們二人就這樣分居著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.59,0:00:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底意味著什麼你明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.20,0:00:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道剛結婚的我每晚隻身一人在床上想些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.63,0:01:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特君你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡邊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上課的時候請安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.42,0:02:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特 午飯有什麼打算
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在來這個島的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的生活費被魚們瓜分了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我把我的便當分給你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 可樂餅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這個月的午飯就由我來做給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常擅長做可樂餅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做的可樂餅真的很好吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡邊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請叫我Mrs渡邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在教師裡請不要剪頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都這麼死板呢 委員長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人 請不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一會就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好的 會打掃乾淨的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特君你最近缺錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不介意的話 今天放學後來我家打工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 是打掃泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正愁著人手不夠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡邊同學的家是「那個家」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都來的話更是幫了我大忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 和子也能去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:03:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭 諏訪也去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像挺有趣的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然熱烈歡迎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的那麼厲害嗎 你的家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特君你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 不是正停靠在東港嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個超大的……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\c&HF9FCFA&\3c&HDDC064&\be3\blur5}第三話  成人銀行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人妻小姐住在那個豪華客船賓館裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是 那個船整個都是渡邊同學的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是結婚的時候她的丈夫買給她的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 你也來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法啊 要乖乖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨 今天拜託各位了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人 您丈夫來電話了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 詢問夫人您何時回巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外希望您能盡早回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個害怕寂寞的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請幫我轉告他 我待會聯繫他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}Allo　Simone
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不接電話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我丈夫不怎麼擅長說日語
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我又不怎麼擅長說法語
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣也能結婚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你說的 我那麼年輕又那麼有風韻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我丈夫雖然是大色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也是世界屈指可數的有錢人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且放眼世界 這種組合也算不上不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.90,0:05:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的的確確是被稱作慾望的東西連接在了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠厚臉皮地說出這些話的夫人 我倒是很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「有風韻」這類的詞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日常對話中我是第一次聽到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就拜託大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼棒的船 我有生以來頭一次看見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡好像有什麼……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.24,0:06:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個池子是鱷魚男爵的家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒關係哦 因為鱷魚男爵非常的乖巧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人妻小姐在幹些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是在炒股
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.14,0:06:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}據說渡邊同學每敲動一下鍵盤 就能帶動一個小國的國家預算
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 這麼厲害的她為什麼來這個島呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.63,0:06:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖地呆著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 副部長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.23,0:06:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊啊老鼠！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}(這大概不是老鼠)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隆智 快點把老鼠清理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:06:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副部長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.11,0:07:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.39,0:07:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊 塔科特君也很有劍術心得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 二位來比試一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是打工的一部分嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.42,0:07:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你們不戴上防具就開始嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有劍術的經驗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來也不是不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個每小時多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了的話 打工的工資翻倍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.31,0:07:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以和我隔著玻璃接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不隔玻璃也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊那是 不可以啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩倍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就為了這個條件去比賽嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩倍可是非常誘人的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的啦……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:08:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行 二位都沒露出真本事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是她自己要他們打打看的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是以自我為中心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅星十字團第四隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「成人銀行」代表人 頭取登場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 綺羅星十字團總會開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Filament」又被做掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.06,0:09:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼賠被損壞的cybody
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:10:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有cybody的所有權可是屬於我們「成人銀行」的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.34,0:10:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都沒有認同那一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個 被損壞的cybody可以修復嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很困難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,構成每一台cybody的oreichalkos
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}oreichalkos 古希臘語 古文獻中記載的銅的合金
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準確地說 是具備有金屬屬性的光學有機結晶體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是類似於遺傳因子的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修復的可能性還是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有道伯恩是第三階段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.99,0:10:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那現在還是個迷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是那台cybody的力量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是因為銀河美少年與眾不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由什麼的無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的首要任務是把他打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那個將道伯恩打倒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將會成為我們的領袖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將他打倒的人將會是領袖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是成為領袖 是否可以明確cybody的所有權問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你能夠成為的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賦予我們榮光 賜予銀河美少年毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 隆志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天白天的比試 你為什麼沒有動真格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他算不上個強勁對手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也不是一場值得較真的比試
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 隆志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是你的話 能夠打倒道伯恩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你打倒他不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是打倒道伯恩的團隊而是打倒他的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將會成為綺羅星的領袖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 若是隆智你打敗道伯恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.11,0:11:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隆智將臨架於那個女人之上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人在叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人 泰幣匯率又下降了兩個百分點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.88,0:12:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去把通貨期貨賣掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}期貨是現在進行買賣，但是在將來進行交收或交割的標的物 也可以是金融工具，還可以是金融指標。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等價格下降到現在得三分之一的時候再買回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.55,0:12:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等賺到利潤了 就脫貨求現把
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.55,0:12:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}脫貨求現 即巧妙變賣 從中賺取差價
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在老公他們正在大量地拋售
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會狠狠下降的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就順勢撈一筆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先告辭了 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是你的話 可以打倒道伯恩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是打倒道伯恩的團隊而是打倒他的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.52,0:12:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將會成為綺羅星的領袖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 若是隆智你打敗道伯恩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隆智將臨架於那個女人之上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當領袖的話 我無所謂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打倒道伯恩的話 格蘭托奈爾也會很困擾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}格蘭托奈爾財團 世界級大財團 總帥渡邊雷昂正是其丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我只是要問你這次是不是會發揮全部實力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.48,0:13:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 他怎麼樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 住在魚之行星的手法很嫻熟的漁民
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說Sam啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他最後有沒有和少女一同 在光彩奪目的銀河世界裡暢遊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在魚之行星 駛向銀河世界的航船只有一艘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那艘船卻屬於國王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王的船隻嗎……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的船隻不可能輕易得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有一天 國王貼出了公告
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒烏賊王的並將其藍色的血液帶回來的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:13:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王將會滿足他任何願望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在魚之行星裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.68,0:14:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每到夜裡 烏賊王就會旁若無人地鬧事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.23,0:14:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定不好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年Sam為了能夠得到那艘能駛向銀河世界的船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決心打倒烏賊王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為人生的冒險仍在繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來到這座島上 是不是為了保護那個女孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開啟吧 電力柩！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apprivoiser
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飄舞的雪花是星之碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著天體伸出雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.34,0:15:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短信？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}感受到轉瞬即逝的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特君沒被吻到你放心了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.05,0:15:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}如今的一切盡在黑白畫之中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定覺得塔科特君還行得通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.91,0:15:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.07,0:15:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}悄然凍結的白色吐息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}壓抑在心的話語化為有形
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}只有聚集那份溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是這個嗎……塔科特君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.15,0:16:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}才能為一切籠上光明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.67,0:16:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}被悲傷浸染的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受我的挑戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}嚮往重疊的純白色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要到了晚上就會這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還不按時間給工資啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}我懷抱著無限溫柔的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apprivoiser
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.34,0:16:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}各自踏上征途的路人們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.53,0:16:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}或許素未謀面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}但只要向著那光明前進
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}便會邂逅在銀河的某處
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}滑落之星化作沙塵之霧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}輕輕拂過我的心頭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}安眠時分所見夢想的殘像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.31,0:17:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}一切仍定格在黑白記憶中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颯爽登場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.27,0:17:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道伯恩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Star Sword Ametist
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.67,0:17:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 看來是那個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Star Sword Emlord
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Star Sword……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙也有Star Sword嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第11把呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺得很拚命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密劍術 紙吹雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特君！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:18:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道伯恩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.29,0:19:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是無趣的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行 果然很棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Star Sword Saphiel
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第12把Star Sword！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙刀流
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿手的是雙刀流嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的行動不利是這個原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Τ射線的光芒啊 將銀河充斥吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豪邁銀河十字斬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Τ射線的光芒……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特納西·塔科特君 嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(笨蛋)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(大概行得通吧)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(已發送)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.33,0:21:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊……輸了的話就要還給你是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.12,0:21:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明擁有標誌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.70,0:21:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻故意使用電力柩的感覺如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.30,0:22:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隆智 真是可惜了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.71,0:22:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.84,0:22:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.01,0:22:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.83,0:22:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說我暫時不能回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.86,0:23:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到這座島上來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.60,0:24:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定就是為了來傾聽你歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.03,0:24:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了你的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.76,0:24:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.90,0:24:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 Star Driver 閃亮的塔科特
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.67,0:24:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.23,0:24:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的銀河一定閃爍著耀眼的光輝
